me by the damn head, Tao!

246
00:12:03,916 --> 00:12:04,833
[NOEL]
I think I'm done.

247
00:12:04,916 --> 00:12:06,458
[LITCHI] Hey!
What's the hurry?

248
00:12:06,541 --> 00:12:08,458
[NOEL] Please,
Miss Litchi! Let me go!

249
00:12:09,166 --> 00:12:11,916
[RAGNA] Get the hell
offa me, you crazy beastkin!

250
00:12:19,416 --> 00:12:20,291
[BOTH] Hey!

251
00:12:20,375 --> 00:12:21,291
[laughing]

252
00:12:21,375 --> 00:12:22,750
Idiots.

253
00:12:25,125 --> 00:12:27,416
After this, you can
do as you please.

254
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:28,666
Huh?

255
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:30,583
[LITCHI] I'm gonna do
as I please right now!

256
00:12:30,666 --> 00:12:31,625
[NOEL] Stop it, Miss Litchi!

257
00:12:31,708 --> 00:12:33,500
You're drunk on catnip-water!

258
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,041
Uh!

259
00:12:36,125 --> 00:12:38,375
[NOEL] Huh?

260
00:12:38,458 --> 00:12:39,833
Uh...

261
00:12:43,375 --> 00:12:44,791
Now what?

262
00:12:44,875 --> 00:12:46,791
[LITCHI and TAOKAKA laughing]

263
00:12:46,875 --> 00:12:50,708
[RAGNA yelling]
[LITCHI and TAOKAKA laughing]

264
00:12:54,083 --> 00:12:56,416
[ALL yell]

265
00:13:02,083 --> 00:13:04,291
My goodness! I can't
figure out how

266
00:13:04,375 --> 00:13:06,500
you put up
with Ragna so well!

267
00:13:06,583 --> 00:13:09,375
[NAGO] He does have those
dreamy mismatched eyes--!

268
00:13:09,458 --> 00:13:11,625
[GII and NAGO] Why?

269
00:13:13,083 --> 00:13:14,750
It seems Ragna
the Bloodedge and

270
00:13:14,833 --> 00:13:17,041
Noel Vermillion's
Azures have begun to

271
00:13:17,125 --> 00:13:19,875
react to one another, correct?

272
00:13:19,958 --> 00:13:21,333
Yes.

273
00:13:21,416 --> 00:13:22,541
[VALKENHAYN]
Then all is proceeding

274
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:25,166
as Madam Rachel intended it.

275
00:13:25,250 --> 00:13:27,583
That, we shall
soon discover.

276
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:42,416
"Miracle cure" my ass!

277
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:43,916
So, where do you suppose

278
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:46,000
Miss Litchi and
Taokaka landed?

279
00:13:46,083 --> 00:13:49,000
Who cares? Let's just get
the hell outta these woods.

280
00:13:49,083 --> 00:13:51,208
Seithr's too
thick around here.

281
00:13:54,375 --> 00:13:55,583
[rustling]

282
00:13:55,666 --> 00:13:56,958
[NOEL] Taokaka?

283
00:13:57,041 --> 00:13:59,916
[rustling]

284
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,875
[MONSTER 5A growls]

285
00:14:03,916 --> 00:14:05,708
[MONSTER 5A growls]

286
00:14:05,791 --> 00:14:07,250
We're outta options.

287
00:14:07,333 --> 00:14:09,625
Leave 'em to me!

288
00:14:09,708 --> 00:14:11,875
Bolverk! Come forth!

289
00:14:12,708 --> 00:14:22,708
♪

290
00:14:26,291 --> 00:14:28,000
[RAGNA] What the hell?

291
00:14:31,333 --> 00:14:33,041
[NOEL] I got 'em all!

292
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:35,750
[NOEL] Uh, Ragna?

293
00:14:35,833 --> 00:14:39,708
You idiot! Do you have
any idea what those are?

294
00:14:39,791 --> 00:14:41,166
[NOEL] Huh?

295
00:14:49,958 --> 00:14:53,416
[RACHEL] The Azures will
cleave to and repel each other.

296
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:55,333
Both at once.

297
00:14:57,958 --> 00:15:00,416
You wait for the possibility
that may emerge

298
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:04,458
from such a paradox, is
that not so, Madam Rachel?

299
00:15:04,541 --> 00:15:06,083
Correct.

300
00:15:06,166 --> 00:15:09,791
What follows will bring
its extremes to the future.

301
00:15:09,875 --> 00:15:12,791
Both hope and despair.

302
00:15:12,875 --> 00:15:14,291
Ragna.

303
00:15:15,083 --> 00:15:17,916
[RACHEL] When change
comes, do not fear it.

304
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,375
The day of reckoning is nigh.

305
00:15:20,458 --> 00:15:23,375
Grow wise and
strong while you can.

306
00:15:23,458 --> 00:15:26,833
Lest the world crush
you under its heel.

307
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:30,333
[RAGNA] Saya's face.
Just like the rest of them!

308
00:15:30,416 --> 00:15:32,458
And she's holding
a Nox Nyctores!

309
00:15:33,041 --> 00:15:36,500
[squelching]

310
00:15:36,583 --> 00:15:39,458
[RAGNA] Is she a
Prime Field Device?

311
00:15:42,125 --> 00:15:45,875
[NOEL] Huh?
What's going on?

312
00:15:45,958 --> 00:15:47,916
[RAGNA yells]

313
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,541
[NOEL gasps]

314
00:15:51,250 --> 00:15:52,375
[NOEL] Ragna, I--!

315
00:15:52,458 --> 00:15:55,458
Shut up! Don't say my
name with that face!

316
00:15:55,541 --> 00:15:56,916
[NOEL] Wha...?

317
00:15:58,250 --> 00:15:59,833
[RAGNA scoffs]

318
00:16:07,333 --> 00:16:09,291
[RACHEL] I am a spectator.

319
00:16:09,375 --> 00:16:12,166
With a sigh, I watch
that which transpires

320
00:16:12,250 --> 00:16:15,291
and trace the ripples
to their terminus.

321
00:16:15,375 --> 00:16:17,625
May these ripples
become a wave.

322
00:16:17,708 --> 00:16:19,541
One that will bear
this world aloft

323
00:16:19,625 --> 00:16:22,083
towards an unwritten future.

324
00:16:23,958 --> 00:16:33,875
♪

325
00:16:33,958 --> 00:16:37,333
[YOUNG RAGNA labored breaths]

326
00:16:37,416 --> 00:16:41,083
[RACHEL]
Do you wish to live?

327
00:16:41,166 --> 00:16:42,041
[YOUNG RAGNA] Uh-huh.

328
00:16:42,125 --> 00:16:44,125
[RACHEL] So be it.

329
00:16:52,208 --> 00:16:54,041
[RACHEL] Ragna.

330
00:16:55,250 --> 00:16:59,750
[YOUNG RAGNA screams]

331
00:16:59,833 --> 00:17:02,625
[RACHEL]
Take the Azure Grimoire.

332
00:17:02,708 --> 00:17:04,958
[YOUNG RAGNA groans]

333
00:17:09,583 --> 00:17:11,541
What's happening to me?

334
00:17:12,625 --> 00:17:16,458
[RACHEL] I wonder. To what
end shall you wield it?

335
00:17:20,333 --> 00:17:21,833
Move forward.

336
00:17:21,916 --> 00:17:25,750
And take us into
the unknown. Ragna.

337
00:17:34,666 --> 00:17:36,041
[CHILD groans]

338
00:17:38,083 --> 00:17:40,166
[groans]

339
00:17:44,625 --> 00:17:47,250
I'm so hungry.
Please, mister.

340
00:17:47,333 --> 00:17:49,083
No chance.

341
00:17:54,541 --> 00:17:56,500
Of all the people
who ignored me,

342
00:17:56,583 --> 00:17:58,583
you are the most cold-hearted.

343
00:17:58,666 --> 00:18:01,833
[CHILD] I curse you from the
bottom of my empty stomach!

344
00:18:01,916 --> 00:18:02,916
Take a number.

345
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:03,958
[CHILD] Uh...!

346
00:18:04,041 --> 00:18:05,875
Ladies and
gentlemen, this man is a

347
00:18:05,958 --> 00:18:08,083
despicable villain
who turns a deaf ear

348
00:18:08,166 --> 00:18:09,875
to the pleas
of hungry children!

349
00:18:09,958 --> 00:18:11,916
Behold this menace
to your city!

350
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,041
He's the devil incarnate!

351
00:18:13,125 --> 00:18:15,250
Shut up, kid!
Don't make a scene!

352
00:18:15,333 --> 00:18:17,916
Hard to be quiet on
an empty stomach.

353
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,625
Hint, hint.

354
00:18:23,375 --> 00:18:25,291
[grunts]

355
00:18:30,625 --> 00:18:33,666
I didn't give you my name.
Sorry about that, sir.

356
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:36,875
I'm Sena. Pleased to
meet you, Mr. Bloodedge.

357
00:18:36,958 --> 00:18:40,375
And what do you call
yourself the rest of the time?

358
00:18:40,458 --> 00:18:42,875
There's another soul
rolling around in there.

359
00:18:42,958 --> 00:18:44,875
Do they want dinner, too?

360
00:18:44,958 --> 00:18:46,375
[chuckles]

361
00:18:46,458 --> 00:18:49,500
I was told that you were
too stupid to pick up on it.

362
00:18:49,583 --> 00:18:50,333
[grunts]

363
00:18:50,416 --> 00:18:52,583
Luna come say hello.

364
00:18:54,541 --> 00:18:55,666
Dumbass!

365
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:56,666
Huh?

366
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:58,291
Luna said you're
a dumbass, dumbass!

367
00:18:58,375 --> 00:19:00,208
If you weren't a friend
of Master Jubei's,

368
00:19:00,291 --> 00:19:02,375
she'd punch your
ugly face into next week!

369
00:19:02,458 --> 00:19:04,041
Jubei?
How do you kn--?

370
00:19:04,125 --> 00:19:06,958
Shut your hole!
Dumb Ragna the Pedo-edge!

371
00:19:07,041 --> 00:19:09,416
[RAGNA] That insult
doesn't make any sense!

372
00:19:10,875 --> 00:19:12,916
Oh, an' now you ignore me?

373
00:19:17,375 --> 00:19:19,666
That's a Nox Nyctores.

374
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:21,791
Huh?

375
00:19:21,875 --> 00:19:23,250
[LUNA] Uh.

376
00:19:30,041 --> 00:19:32,916
Don't mind her.
She's very young.

377
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:36,250
While alive, I was known
as Trinity Glassfille.

378
00:19:36,333 --> 00:19:40,000
Trinity, huh? So you
were one of the Six Heroes.

379
00:19:40,083 --> 00:19:43,291
You sensed a Nox Nyctores.
You're very good.

380
00:19:43,375 --> 00:19:45,416
Cut the crap.
You'd have popped out

381
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:47,541
even if I hadn't sensed it.

382
00:19:49,041 --> 00:19:51,041
So, we takin'
this outside?

383
00:19:51,125 --> 00:19:52,750
[chuckles]

384
00:19:52,833 --> 00:19:55,458
Your wariness
is understandable.

385
00:19:55,541 --> 00:19:59,166
Believe me when I say I have
no intention of fighting you.

386
00:19:59,250 --> 00:20:03,041
Ragna, I come here
to deliver a warning.

387
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:08,708
Under no circumstance
must you fight Yuuki Terumi.

388
00:20:08,791 --> 00:20:11,000
With the Azure
Grimoire as it is,

389
00:20:11,083 --> 00:20:12,916
you will surely perish.

390
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:15,208
Listen! I can
beat that bastard--!

391
00:20:17,166 --> 00:20:19,166
Can't I?

392
00:20:29,125 --> 00:20:30,958
Luna couldn't
eat another bite!

393
00:20:31,041 --> 00:20:32,958
Later, perv!

394
00:20:33,041 --> 00:20:35,625
[SENA] Thank you very
much for the meal.

395
00:20:37,791 --> 00:20:40,625
If it ain't one thing,
it's another.

396
00:20:45,416 --> 00:20:47,083
Hmmm.

397
00:20:49,041 --> 00:20:52,250
Ragna.
This is Tager, over.

398
00:20:52,333 --> 00:20:54,708
Do you copy, Kokonoe?

399
00:20:54,791 --> 00:20:56,125
[KOKONOE]
The signal feed is crap,

400
00:20:56,208 --> 00:20:58,250
but I'll live. What's up?

401
00:20:58,333 --> 00:21:01,708
I found an Azure, but not
the one you sent me for.

402
00:21:01,791 --> 00:21:03,458
[KOKONOE] Ragna
the Bloodedge, huh?

403
00:21:03,541 --> 00:21:07,416
Affirmative, and there's no
sign of Noel Vermillion yet.

404
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,625
Your call.

405
00:21:08,708 --> 00:21:11,208
[KOKONOE] Well, when
life gives you lemons.

406
00:21:11,291 --> 00:21:12,791
[laughs intensely]

407
00:21:12,875 --> 00:21:14,083
Uh, Kokonoe?

408
00:21:14,166 --> 00:21:16,125
[KOKONOE] Park your
big red ass where it is.

409
00:21:16,208 --> 00:21:17,916
Time for a test-drive.

410
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:20,083
What do you mean
"a test drive"?

411
00:21:20,166 --> 00:21:21,875
[KOKONOE] Here goes nothing!

412
00:21:29,083 --> 00:21:32,166
Spatial transfer complete.

413
00:21:32,250 --> 00:21:35,708
Loading. Loading. Ready.

414
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:09,500
[SENA] The title of
the next episode is--

415
00:23:09,583 --> 00:23:10,833
[TAOKAKA] Om-noms!

416
00:23:10,916 --> 00:23:12,416
[LUNA] We totally hustled
that perv for a meal!

417
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:13,583
[SENA] It's "False World."

418
00:23:13,666 --> 00:23:14,791
[TAOKAKA]
Good Guy's no perv!

419
00:23:14,875 --> 00:23:16,458
[LUNA] Yeah, says you!

